<p><a href="#sdfootnote11anc" name="sdfootnote11sym">11</a> Ibid., 116.</p>
<p><a href="#sdfootnote12anc" name="sdfootnote12sym">12</a> See: Bińczyk, <em>Epoka człowieka</em>, 30, 113–114, 177.</p>
<p><a href="#sdfootnote13anc" name="sdfootnote13sym">13</a> McBrien, “Accumulating Extinction,” 116.</p>
